# Committed, build-time public config (Vite inlines VITE_* into the browser bundle).
# Safe to commit: this is a public URL, not a secret. Secrets (LLM_API_KEY) must
# NOT go here — keep those in the Netlify/Render dashboards.

# Live-run backend (Render). The app defaults its "backend URL" to this, so the
# top-bar pill goes green and Run is real without editing Settings.
VITE_BACKEND_URL=https://crewai-live-run.onrender.com
